rows.label: tlk42300013_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I am practicing speaking in the
manner of ancient Nopon.

rows.label: tlk42300013_02_msg0002
rows.name:
This may be against the wishes
of the revered Captain Nopopon...

rows.label: tlk42300013_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But I feel it is a necessity in order to
obtain a fuller understanding of the
intricacies of Nopon history.

rows.label: tlk42300013_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh... Rododo not able
take it any more! Modern Nopon talk
come so much more natural!
